  "keyFeatures": [
    "1:1 movement simulation engine covering all Minecraft physics edge cases",
    "Fully asynchronous and multithreaded design for high-performance servers",
    "Per-player world replication with lag compensation",
    "Support for Minecraft 1.8–1.21 across Bukkit, Paper, Folia, and Fabric",
    "Predictive checks for reach, timer, speed, knockback, and more",
    "Configurable punishment system with Discord webhook and proxy alert support",
    "Plugin API for third-party integration and custom check development",
    "Geyser/Floodgate compatibility with full Bedrock player exemption"
